activity than an all you can eat resteraunt near a fat farm.  She
instinctively cloaked to hide her identity. She now appeared to be no larger
than a sparrow. She  took extra measures by flying low to the ground making
herself appear to be an even more natural bird. The hawk landed on the
charred Spanish shore and scanned outward into the horizon. What she saw
scared her. She detected a warship docked near an island miles offshore. She
saw the shield surrounding the base and knew that she was in for more than
she knew. She tried to transform but a twinge of pain shot through her. She
tried again transforming to robot mode. She could see that the fur of her
wolf mode, and feathers of her hawk mode hadn&#39;t changed like they had
before. The femm placed a recorder under part of the charred beach and set
the message. &quot;I&#39;ve reached the shoreline, I&#39;m not sure if this is the right
place but it&#39;s security is very detailed. I&#39;m going in, I&#39;ll report next
time I get the chance.&quot; the bot didn&#39;t leave a name, she didn&#39;t want to lose
any advantage if the message was intercepted. &quot;Relay message in one hour.&quot;
She left the instructions to allow her enough time to get away in case it&#39;s
found or intercepted.  Silver Scout again transformed to hawk mode and
started flying out to sea.
